  "title": "Question on the page \"pagination\"",
  "body": "Hi! I have a documentation issue on InstantSearch.js. I could not find what I was looking for on the page \"[pagination](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/widgets/pagination.html)\".\r\n\r\n<!-- Describe what you're looking for here. -->\r\n\r\nI am only returning 1 or 2 hits but the pagination is still showing as a hyperlinked integer of \"1\". If you looked at the searchParameters.hitsPerPage and found that hits are less that this value, hide the pagination.",
